f:\Bbb R^n\to\Bbb R
  f(x) = \begin{cases}\sin\left(\frac{1}{\|x\|}\right)\|x\|^{-n-\arctan(\|x\|-1)}  & x\not=0 \\ 0 & x=0  \\ \end{cases}
A_k:=\{x\in\Bbb R^n:\frac{1}{k}\le \|x\|\le k\}
A_k\subset A_{k+1}
\cup_{k\in\Bbb N} A_k=\Bbb R^n-\{0\}
A_k
k\in\Bbb N
f|_{A_k}(x)=\begin{cases} \sin\left(\frac{1}{\|x\|}\right)\|x\|^{-n-\arctan(\|x\|-1)} & \|x\|\in[1/k,k] \\ 0 & \|x\|\not\in[1/k,k] \end{cases}
